    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> mooli slaw mix</strong> to a large bowl with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>half</strong> your <strong>black</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong> (save the rest for later!) and the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>cucumber matchsticks </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Toss everything together – this is your <strong>sesame lime slaw</strong></p>",
