      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> honey</strong> to a separate bowl with your <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) <strong>sesame oil</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and<strong> </strong>a squeeze of <strong>lime juice</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>honey sriracha glaze</strong></p>",
