    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the salmon is cooked through, transfer to a clean board (remove the pan from the heat and reserve)</p><p>Remove and discard the skin, then break the <strong>cooked salmon</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
